<docs>
	<doc for="ISqlReader">
		<summary>
			<para>Provides a method of reading a forward-only, read-only 
      stream of rows from a SQL Server database.</para>
		</summary>
		<remarks>
			<para>The <see cref="System.Data.ISqlReader"/> interface inherits from the <see cref="System.Data.IDataReader"/> 
interface and allows a .NET data provider to create a DataReader for use
with a SQL Server database. </para>
		</remarks>
	</doc></docs>
